snippet.title: Evil Inside - Announcement Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Evil Inside is coming to PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4 on March 25th 2021

Evil Inside is a first-person psychological horror game. After the death of his mother and the arrest of his father for it, Mark decides to contact her using the Spiritual board. But it fades away, and here is when all begins... Mark will face his greatest fears to discover the truth.

---------

Read more about the game on: https://www.jandusoft.com 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/JanduSoft
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JanduSoft
